# kiss-containers

podman, podman-compose, and their dependencies
aiming for rootless, simple containerization

## packages

 podman: rootless, daemonless docker replacement
 podman-compose: simple, docker-compose compatible multi-container tool

## tooling

 crun
 runc

## dependencies

 cni-plugins
 conmon
 fuse-overlayfs
 go-md2man
 libcap
 skopeo
 slirp4netns-bin
 yajl
